/remove_moderator "name" (Remove a moderator from a private chat channel, creators only)
/add_ban "name" (Add a ban on a user in a private chat channel, moderators only)
/remove_ban "name" (Remove a ban on a user in a private chat channel, moderators only)
/status (Get information on the current channel)
